summary: The video promotes a travel deal for a round-trip airline pass to Tahiti, Paris, Auckland, and Tokyo for $1,525 per person. It highlights the limited availability of 250 passes and the requirement to fly out of LAX or Seattle. The pass goes on sale on November 25th at 9 a.m. Pacific time.
keywords: airline pass, Tahiti, Paris, Auckland, Tokyo, $1525, LAX, Seattle, November 25th, 9am PST, 250 passes, Air Tahiti Nui
